content.p: We provide a range of services to veterinary professionals and businesses. Working with our specialist teams can help strengthen your workforce and improve the care you provide. For businesses and individuals looking to enhance their skills and improve their care Full biopsy and necropsy services for practices and animal charities Detailed analysis of animals nutrition, including blood, tissue, urine and food If you have a question about any of our services for business please get in touch with the relevant team. telephone: +44 (0)115 951 6116 fax: +44 (0)115 951 6415 email: veterinary-enquiries@nottingham.ac.uk
